{"tid":309443,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"請珍惜朗尼...（認真）","createTime":"2017-07-05T04:44:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-06T09:25:19.000Z","uid":31314,"like":13,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"76b58b58a063f0829d6b014f6a5aa88281c65327","tid":309443,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T04:44:58.000Z","msg":"細個開始睇波果陣好撚憎49000，覺得史譚、簡東拿、堅尼好拎茅（當年堅尼一野踢低holland），次次進攻都好似教科書一樣既戰術好悶<br />\n到佢地退晒休，先知果D老練既技術／走位係好野黎<br />\n史高斯既獨特節奏、雲達沙既神救、費格遜對勝利既執著，都係到退休／收左皮先發現佢地原來咁撚勁<br />\n連登仔好多人都反朗尼，但係老實講佢既控波技術、遠射能力、對比賽既執著，冇人比得上佢（我覺得依家朗尼&gt;&gt;C朗）<br />\n我諗朗尼最多都係打多1、2年就退休，其實睇得1場得1場，好好珍惜<br />\n利申：阿仙姑不敗年代雲加迷"},{"pid":"12b3438a4de61980b3411c4342badf509eca4326","tid":309443,"uid":30773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T04:46:31.000Z","msg":"假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbd19cd9dfc97747f87482c3010cd783f02e903a","tid":309443,"uid":3003,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T04:46:49.000Z","msg":"十卜。。。"},{"pid":"406738fd67e081acbc41d1024b6b2d28c832fc97","tid":309443,"uid":51114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T04:51:28.000Z","msg":"ching six ball"},{"pid":"2c9ab2e0f3c6644036d053b1df9a9777159d276e","tid":309443,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T04:53:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你就假膠，我不嬲迷朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c790b991e8e4ef67a90eed3e896e07aaa025bd","tid":309443,"uid":1289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T04:59:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b42a4ff36206641c109f06f6723d276b59f9b6dc","tid":309443,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T05:10:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>朗隊真係要走？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\